{"tid":2063640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民女團隊辦展覽：我哋打不死","createTime":"2020-06-14T07:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T07:58:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c82c1131e4bc1ca85299ace244c621c2af278c99","tid":2063640,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:42:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200614/CG5LN6PFKAETTTN7XEMGCKDORQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200614%2FCG5LN6PFKAETTTN7XEMGCKDORQ%2F&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJh1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=96b456bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200614%2FCG5LN6PFKAETTTN7XEMGCKDORQ%2F&h=7c7df699\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200614/CG5LN6PFKAETTTN7XEMGCKDORQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n民女團隊辦展覽：我哋打不死<br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/77YGMVQDXD64FTNKT5CN2M5HHE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F77YGMVQDXD64FTNKT5CN2M5HHE.jpg&h=235039ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民主女神像上半身以3D打印技術修復展出，用手撐天花板的姿態寓意抵抗北京壓力。<br />\n<br />\n反送中運動中，抗爭圖騰湧現，Pepe蛙、連狗、連豬，還有香港民主女神像（民女）。民女於去年8月出自一眾連登討論區網民集體創作，後來眾籌製作成4米高巨型雕塑「出席」多場集會活動；10月完成「登上」獅子山壯舉，甚至多番在外媒鎂光燈下亮相。今年5月底，民女團隊在深水埗一間cafe二樓舉行了一場主題展覽，發言人Flash指，和理非集會多個月來被警方打壓，令民女無法出動，團隊惟有透過展覽激勵同路人，同時以商業方式營運，將收益支援抗爭者。<br />\n<br />\n展覽以香港民主女神像為主題，名為「我哋仲未__ __展」，橫線上填寫甚麼？全由參觀者決定，人們紛紛用便利貼寫上不同字眼：屈服、沉寂、放棄&hellip;&hellip;踏上cafe二樓，就見到約2米高的全白色民女上半身佔據近半個展場，雕像一手撐住天花板，「想講香港人一直撐住由上面、北方而嚟嘅政府壓力、打壓」，Flash說。<br />\n<br />\n回想去年10月，團隊曾出動幾十人將民女合力抬上獅子山，但不消半日便遭人破壞和塗污，這次展出將上次被................好，我哋都係唔會死，會返嚟，再出聲同你死過，呢個係象徵意義，希望參觀者睇到有所鼓舞。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OETPRHXAECYTPKLKTQBTWF5X7M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOETPRHXAECYTPKLKTQBTWF5X7M.jpg&h=4ec5e528&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFlash設計的展板告訴參觀者民女像登上獅子山過程。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OY4JJAKPCIBT7WQRZRCVKSCYW4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOY4JJAKPCIBT7WQRZRCVKSCYW4.jpg&h=3d0e9a66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n團隊邀請何兆基、Afterworkshop等多位本地藝術家創作民女像，拍賣收益扣除成本捐予612人道基金。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n商業營運助持久<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：藝術教授黃照達：鼓動人心兼療癒<br />\n<br />\n訪問當日不是公眾假期，但排隊入場的參觀者仍擠滿大門。曾否擔心設展會遭建制人士騷擾？Flash稱不太擔心，......................你張牌，唔知啦」，由於團隊本來想將民女下半身復修，並放置在cafe一樓，最終因為不想影響場主，只在二樓放置大型展品。<br />\n<br />\n「民女只係一個工具，佢唔係一個終極目標，係我哋未爭取到要做嘅嘢，就要利用佢做啲好爆嘅嘢，例如上獅子山，................作了多個迷你版女神像，讓人帶去全球各地，甚至北京天安門廣場上打卡。<br />\n<br />\n本身也是設計師的Flash透露，團隊成員來自五湖四海和各行業，部份人長居海外，當中有任職消防員、醫護.....................本後收益將全數捐予612人道支援基金會等多個聲援抗爭者組織，「可能幾隻（藝術品）賣幾萬蚊，又幫到抗爭者打多一場官司」。<br />\n<br />\n早在「黃色經濟圈」概念誕生前，團隊已決定以商業營運，將利潤聘請抗爭者，展覽中公佈相關數字，暫時已支出一百萬，支援超過260人，當中包括向20位抗爭者提供住屋、電腦用品等生活支援，另外聘請40名長期員工及200位臨時工，前者負責做3D打印、包裝，「有義賣點幫手派貨、跟貨車、自己揸車，好多嘢都可以貢獻到，都會教佢哋用3D printer、打磨」，而臨時工則主力包裝展覽中出售的產品，讓這場長期戰能持續下去。"},{"pid":"7de4a2611ee3c0bebf7fd91b589bed43ee85ae08","tid":2063640,"uid":8948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:47:03.000Z","msg":"每個人都盡力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持"},{"pid":"9722713c34a84ede840e3fca80f1fdb597fed5d5","tid":2063640,"uid":29823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:47:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0db7a5de070ed9c8da2f5b71f4a40fd555717178","tid":2063640,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7de4a2611ee3c0bebf7fd91b589bed43ee85ae08","tid":2063640,"uid":8948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:47:03.000Z","msg":"每個人都盡力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:48:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f624f66c2c5956bc53512d1fb588812f340337","tid":2063640,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}